thread.title: Devi
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Devi

author: Devi
title: Devi
text:
I placed an order at 3:30pm requesting next day delivery to VA, and to FL. They delivered on both counts. And having experienced Maine lobster first hand, they did not disappoint.
I received the freshest, sweetest, most succulent lobster meat! I could have been right there in Portland, it was that good. And word from Miami? They were blown away too.
Will definitely order again.
